{
  "stem": "5639.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He admired their sense of organization, their sense of order.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He admired their cleanness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He admired their reliability.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember that my brother, for his bar mitzvah, got the collected works of Goethe and Schiller in gothic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had-- my father had business in connection-- well, interests actually because he had real estate in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He made very frequent trips to  Berlin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he spoke and wrote German much better than he did Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father had a normal Jewish education, but not a higher education.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was what you would call now a silent partner with his cousin in a coal mine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a coal-mining district, I might as well add.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the potbelly of-- of Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The biggest deposits of coal in Poland were in that district.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was quite sufficient for a very comfortable living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, the fact that we had-- [INAUDIBLE] --real estate in Germany, which provided us with a handsome-- I imagine that must have been quite handsome--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--income.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very frequently.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From '33 he was not restricted, but his trips were less frequent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the type of changes-- he said, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For instance, his restaurant where he used to go, tailor-- stop?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
